{"type":null,"faqId":10031,"title":"G6-U00WLAN待机的时候会自动断开，怎么解决，手机默认是什么设置？","answer":"&nbsp;\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">这个问题是休眠策略的问题。进入的方法：在主屏幕，点击<b>设置</b><span>-&gt;<b>WLAN</b></span>，再点击<span></span>并进入<b>高级</b><span>-&gt;</span><b>在休眠状态下保持<span>WLAN</span>连接</b>，设置为“始终”。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">注：手机默认设置是<b>仅限充电时</b>，也就是在充电状态下一直连接。如果调整休眠策略就会使得在待机时自动断开。<span>3</span>个选项的含义如下：</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>&nbsp;</span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">从不（会增加数据流量）</span></b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">：屏幕关闭</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">分钟后进入休眠。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">仅限充电时</span></b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">：只有在充电状态下才不进入休眠。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">始终</span></b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">：一直不会进入休眠。<span></span></span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"632","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1396496971000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":14,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"WLAN","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}